    @DefaultProperty(value="content")
public class DockablePane
extends javafx.scene.control.Control
implements Dockable
    A container which can be docked in the Docking System. TODO: Should this class extend javafx.scene.layout.Pane instead of Control? Note: This class might be removed in the future!

    puce
